# Git commit messages

Do **not** add `Co-authored-by:` (or similar) trailers naming Cursor, Claude, Copilot, or any other AI tool. The human author owns the commits.

When suggesting commit messages, squash messages, or `git commit` bodies, omit trailer blocks that attribute authorship to assistants.
